query:
SELECT ne.id, ne.inspectionId, ne.nozzleNumber, ne.nozzleDescription, ne.nominalSize, ne.schedule, ne.actualThickness, ne.minRequiredThickness, ne.status
FROM nozzleEvaluations ne
WHERE ne.inspectionId IN (SELECT id FROM inspections WHERE vesselTagNumber LIKE '%57-11-001%')
ORDER BY ne.nozzleNumber;
